567
00:29:32,562 --> 00:29:35,065
- [Hayoung] Sister, why are you here now? - [Haran] No, I’m a little…

568
00:29:35,148 --> 00:29:36,692
-There's chalk on your face... - [Hadam] Yugyeom!

569
00:29:36,775 --> 00:29:37,693
