710
00:37:36,546 --> 00:37:38,339
I was rude because I couldn't manage my condition.

711
00:37:39,466 --> 00:37:41,551
But what should I do?

712
00:37:41,634 --> 00:37:42,969
I'll see Changmo later.

713
00:37:43,052 --> 00:37:46,014
