731
00:38:53,957 --> 00:38:54,791
Hadam!

732
00:38:54,874 --> 00:38:56,334
Cha Yugyeom, how did you meet Han Sora…

733
00:38:56,417 --> 00:38:57,669
[Haran] Hadam

734
00:39:00,588 --> 00:39:03,258
-Why is my eldest sister here? - [Hayoung] I have one too.

735
00:39:06,219 --> 00:39:09,097
[Hadam] What? You just waited in front of the school?

736
00:39:09,180 --> 00:39:10,515
Even though you don’t know Yugyeom’s face?

737
00:39:10,598 --> 00:39:14,060
