766
00:40:26,799 --> 00:40:28,259
Even when it’s not supposed to be, it comes suddenly

767
00:40:30,386 --> 00:40:31,930
Like the day I first met you

768
00:40:33,848 --> 00:40:35,558
Have you been to the hospital?

769
00:40:37,268 --> 00:40:40,855
I received a suspicious finding at a center that conducted a simple examination.

770
00:40:41,439 --> 00:40:44,776
I made an appointment for a detailed evaluation and will be tested in a few weeks.

771
00:40:46,903 --> 00:40:48,738
But if you live around my age

772
