1302
01:06:01,207 --> 01:06:03,793
[Jomo Chan] Right? What do you like about designer Song?

1303
01:06:04,419 --> 01:06:05,670
[Chan] It’s not really

1304
01:06:06,421 --> 01:06:07,839
He's someone I shouldn't like.

1305
01:06:09,090 --> 01:06:11,009
