1306
01:06:12,719 --> 01:06:14,971
hey! You couldn't possibly date a married woman, huh?

1307
01:06:15,054 --> 01:06:16,556
[Chan] Oh, I’m not a married woman.

1308
01:06:16,639 --> 01:06:19,184
[Jomo Chan] No, then why are you saying I shouldn’t like it, huh?

1309
01:06:19,267 --> 01:06:21,311
Grandma, can I get that towel please?

1310
01:06:21,394 --> 01:06:23,855
[Jomo Chan] Uh, uh, yes.

1311
01:06:23,938 --> 01:06:26,232
Sorry, I heard it by chance.

1312
01:06:26,858 --> 01:06:29,110
But I can't understand it

1313
01:06:29,819 --> 01:06:32,071
It’s not that the person I like is ‘not’.

1314
01:06:32,155 --> 01:06:34,532
If you like someone, you are 'not okay'.

1315
01:06:34,616 --> 01:06:36,159
Because the words are a bit strange

1316
01:06:42,081 --> 01:06:43,541
I'm not even a married woman

1317
01:06:43,625 --> 01:06:46,794
If I were to ask, well, there is nothing to worry about.

1318
01:06:47,629 --> 01:06:49,214
What does that mean?

1319
01:06:53,843 --> 01:06:56,429
Oh, I don't mean to argue.

1320
01:06:56,512 --> 01:06:57,889
I'm really just curious

1321
01:06:57,972 --> 01:06:59,641
Then can I like it?

1322
01:07:01,684 --> 01:07:03,269
[Music fades]

1323
01:07:27,085 --> 01:07:29,087
[♪ Emotional music]

1324
01:08:08,126 --> 01:08:11,129
[Haran] The person who gave me that pen is dead.

1325
01:08:11,671 --> 01:08:15,425
[Chan] What else happened besides the explosion?

1326
01:08:15,508 --> 01:08:17,844
[Haran] I’m honestly curious.

1327
01:08:17,927 --> 01:08:20,888
I feel like I'm only telling half the story.

1328
01:08:20,972 --> 01:08:22,765
[Chan] Things of the past

1329
01:08:22,849 --> 01:08:26,394
It may not be as beautiful as you remember

1330
01:08:27,061 --> 01:08:29,731
[Chan] If you get it right, I’ll explain everything.

1331
01:08:29,814 --> 01:08:33,526
Today is the day I want to talk about everything.

1332
01:08:34,610 --> 01:08:35,778
[Haran] Hall

1333
01:08:36,362 --> 01:08:37,488
[Chan] Hall

1334
01:08:41,659 --> 01:08:43,494
[♪ Theme song]

